{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/useful-app/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b98af55f-9e64-51b3-bd18-59d8965a10d2","excerpt":"今回は、いつもお世話になっているアプリたちを紹介します。 Macに入れているアプリ 私はMac愛用者です。\n相棒は、Mac Book Pro (Retina 13inch Mid 2014)。メモリーは16GB。 Alfred 3 これはMacを使っている人にはぜひ入れていただきたいです。  Ctrl +Space…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/useful-app/#mac%E3%81%AB%E5%85%A5%E3%82%8C%E3%81%A6%E3%81%84%E3%82%8B%E3%82%A2%E3%83%97%E3%83%AA\">Macに入れているアプリ</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#alfred-3\">Alfred 3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#mindnode\">MindNode</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/useful-app/#ipad%E3%81%AB%E3%81%84%E3%82%8C%E3%81%A6%E3%82%8B%E3%82%82%E3%81%AE\">iPadにいれてるもの</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#good-notes-5\">Good Notes 5</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#documents-by-readdle\">Documents by Readdle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#kindle\">Kindle</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/useful-app/#iphone%E3%81%AB%E3%81%84%E3%82%8C%E3%81%A6%E3%81%84%E3%82%8B%E3%82%82%E3%81%AE\">iPhoneにいれているもの</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#bear\">Bear</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#tick-tick\">Tick Tick</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#feedly\">Feedly</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/useful-app/#%E3%83%87%E3%83%BC%E3%82%BF%E5%85%B1%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A8\">データ共有編</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#air-drop\">Air Drop</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#google-drive\">Google Drive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#icloud-drive\">iCloud Drive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#evernote\">Evernote</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/useful-app/#pocket\">Pocket</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<p>今回は、いつもお世話になっているアプリたちを紹介します。</p>\n<h2 id=\"macに入れているアプリ\" style=\"position:relative;\">Macに入れているアプリ</h2>\n<p>私はMac愛用者です。\n相棒は、Mac Book Pro (Retina 13inch Mid 2014)。メモリーは16GB。</p>\n<h3 id=\"alfred-3\" style=\"position:relative;\">Alfred 3</h3>\n<p>これはMacを使っている人にはぜひ入れていただきたいです。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.999999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Alfred3\"\n        title=\"Alfred3\"\n        src=\"/static/b198bb095b57461369450a4bf3e451e3/4b190/ss_alfred_01_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b198bb095b57461369450a4bf3e451e3/e07e9/ss_alfred_01_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/b198bb095b57461369450a4bf3e451e3/066f9/ss_alfred_01_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/b198bb095b57461369450a4bf3e451e3/4b190/ss_alfred_01_20191115.jpg 800w,\n/static/b198bb095b57461369450a4bf3e451e3/a2510/ss_alfred_01_20191115.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Ctrl +Spaceをおすと、検索バーが出てきます。\nここにソフト名を入れて、Enterを押すと、そのままソフトを開くことができるんです。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Alfred3\"\n        title=\"Alfred3\"\n        src=\"/static/eef8d4ddae0444229c242815df47be29/4b190/ss_alfred_02_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eef8d4ddae0444229c242815df47be29/e07e9/ss_alfred_02_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/eef8d4ddae0444229c242815df47be29/066f9/ss_alfred_02_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/eef8d4ddae0444229c242815df47be29/4b190/ss_alfred_02_20191115.jpg 800w,\n/static/eef8d4ddae0444229c242815df47be29/a2510/ss_alfred_02_20191115.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p> 「’」のあとに続けてファイル名を入れれば、ファイルを開くこともできます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 27%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Alfred3\"\n        title=\"Alfred3\"\n        src=\"/static/2d47b92ef88ee041c58e79bfe142bef0/4b190/ss_alfred_03_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2d47b92ef88ee041c58e79bfe142bef0/e07e9/ss_alfred_03_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/2d47b92ef88ee041c58e79bfe142bef0/066f9/ss_alfred_03_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/2d47b92ef88ee041c58e79bfe142bef0/4b190/ss_alfred_03_20191115.jpg 800w,\n/static/2d47b92ef88ee041c58e79bfe142bef0/a2510/ss_alfred_03_20191115.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>これがあるかないかで作業効率が全然違う😁</p>\n<h3 id=\"mindnode\" style=\"position:relative;\">MindNode</h3>\n<p>マインドマップ を作るためのアプリです。\n有料ですが、マインドマップ のアプリはこれが最高です。\nUIが素晴らしい。すごく使いやすい。iPadにも入れています。\n情報を視覚的に整理できるので考え事をする時に開いています。</p>\n<p>例えば、ホームページやブログのサイトマップに\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"コンテンツマップ\"\n        title=\"コンテンツマップ\"\n        src=\"/static/1ecd105b6400ae996acf4d1112283f33/7bf67/SS-sitemap-01.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1ecd105b6400ae996acf4d1112283f33/e07e9/SS-sitemap-01.jpg 200w,\n/static/1ecd105b6400ae996acf4d1112283f33/066f9/SS-sitemap-01.jpg 400w,\n/static/1ecd105b6400ae996acf4d1112283f33/7bf67/SS-sitemap-01.jpg 680w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>本の内容整理に\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"本の内容整理\"\n        title=\"本の内容整理\"\n        src=\"/static/e0f0d2ef7b51378e97e35a49e496b8f1/4b190/ss_mindnode_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e0f0d2ef7b51378e97e35a49e496b8f1/e07e9/ss_mindnode_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/e0f0d2ef7b51378e97e35a49e496b8f1/066f9/ss_mindnode_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/e0f0d2ef7b51378e97e35a49e496b8f1/4b190/ss_mindnode_20191115.jpg 800w,\n/static/e0f0d2ef7b51378e97e35a49e496b8f1/a2510/ss_mindnode_20191115.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple113/v4/ee/e1/04/eee104b6-f020-4c55-133f-5c8faf676b4d/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"MindNode &#x2013; Mind Map\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">MindNode &#x2013; Mind Map</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">IdeasOnCanvas GmbH</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/mindnode-mind-map/id1218718027?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"ipadにいれてるもの\" style=\"position:relative;\">iPadにいれてるもの</h2>\n<p>打ち合わせのために、毎回、Mac Book Proを持ち運ぶのは重い…。それで、去年、iPadを書いました♪</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Apple Pencilと合わせて、ノートとして使えること</li>\n<li>iPhoneよりも画面が大きいので、電子書籍が読みやすい</li>\n<li>相手にも画面を見せやすい</li>\n</ul>\n<p>買ってよかった＾＾</p>\n<h3 id=\"good-notes-5\" style=\"position:relative;\">Good Notes 5</h3>\n<p>手書きのノートアプリです。会議のメモに使っています。</p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/8e/db/d0/8edbd0ad-ed48-22d0-edd6-be49c3375bb2/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"GoodNotes 5\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">GoodNotes 5</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">Time Base Technology Limited</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#xA5;980</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/goodnotes-5/id1444383602?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<h3 id=\"documents-by-readdle\" style=\"position:relative;\">Documents by Readdle</h3>\n<p>端末上の書類を一括で管理できるアプリ。\nGoogle DriveやiCloud Driveも、このアプリから開けます。\nZIPファイルを解凍したりもできるので便利。</p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is5-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/ad/70/ac/ad70acc5-a606-7b3b-94ac-620834f95f2f/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"Documents by Readdle\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">Documents by Readdle</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">Readdle Inc.</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/documents-by-readdle/id364901807?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<h3 id=\"kindle\" style=\"position:relative;\">Kindle</h3>\n<p>普通に漫画を読んだり。</p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple113/v4/5d/ba/44/5dba44df-8ad7-8ed0-bef4-7f0c398d783a/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"Kindle\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">Kindle</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">AMZN Mobile LLC</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/kindle/id302584613?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<p>IT系の本はサイズが大きいし、重いもの。\n分厚い本を開いたり閉じたりするのも面倒だし。\niPadで複数の本を調べたり、付箋貼ったページを行き来できる。</p>\n<p>横でiPadを見つつ、Macで操作できるのが助かってます。\nほんと、Web系の書類は全部電子化してほしい…。</p>\n<h2 id=\"iphoneにいれているもの\" style=\"position:relative;\">iPhoneにいれているもの</h2>\n<h3 id=\"bear\" style=\"position:relative;\">Bear</h3>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is5-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/25/87/40/25874033-d5f1-0fc1-45ce-2c2c3a51cba1/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"Bear - &#x30D7;&#x30E9;&#x30A4;&#x30D9;&#x30FC;&#x30C8;&#x30E1;&#x30E2;\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">Bear - &#x30D7;&#x30E9;&#x30A4;&#x30D9;&#x30FC;&#x30C8;&#x30E1;&#x30E2;</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">Shiny Frog Ltd.</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/bear-%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2582%25A4%25E3%2583%2599%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%2588%25E3%2583%25A1%25E3%2583%25A2/id1016366447?uo=4\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<p>ブログや文章を書くときのテキストエディタ。\nもう使いやすくて、iPhoneだけでなく、MacやiPadにもいれています。</p>\n<p>Markdownで文章をかけるのがありがたい！\n<a href=\"/markdown/\">Markdownを知ってから、ブログ執筆がめっちゃスピードアップした</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"tick-tick\" style=\"position:relative;\">Tick Tick</h3>\n<p>todoや予定を管理するためのアプリです。\nEventもTodoもここに入れています。</p>\n<p>UIがすごい好きなんです。見やすい。\nTodoを完了した時の音がマリオのコインをゲットしたときの音に似てて、やったぜ感があります😁</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 171.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pomo\"\n        title=\"Pomo\"\n        src=\"/static/72a70d4350927b90460493531917cddd/acb04/ss_ticktick_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/72a70d4350927b90460493531917cddd/e07e9/ss_ticktick_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/72a70d4350927b90460493531917cddd/066f9/ss_ticktick_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/72a70d4350927b90460493531917cddd/acb04/ss_ticktick_20191115.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\nPomoという２５分間のタイマー付きなので、集中して作業するときにも</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 173.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Tick Tick\"\n        title=\"Tick Tick\"\n        src=\"/static/0c3c1c34b893325e2535d445f852be70/acb04/ss_ticktick_pomo_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0c3c1c34b893325e2535d445f852be70/e07e9/ss_ticktick_pomo_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/0c3c1c34b893325e2535d445f852be70/066f9/ss_ticktick_pomo_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/0c3c1c34b893325e2535d445f852be70/acb04/ss_ticktick_pomo_20191115.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n毎日やる行動も登録できるので、習慣化にもおすすめ。</p>\n<p><img src=\"ss_ticktick_habit_20191115-1.jpg\" alt=\"Tick Tick\"></p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple114/v4/ad/80/3d/ad803dac-8cd5-5eed-f1f8-3c9ebce0d2f1/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"ticktick-&#x30B7;&#x30F3;&#x30D7;&#x30EB;&#x306A;todo&#x30EA;&#x30B9;&#x30C8;&#xFF06;&#x30BF;&#x30B9;&#x30AF;&#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">ticktick-&#x30B7;&#x30F3;&#x30D7;&#x30EB;&#x306A;todo&#x30EA;&#x30B9;&#x30C8;&#xFF06;&#x30BF;&#x30B9;&#x30AF;&#x7BA1;&#x7406;&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">Appest Limited</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/ticktick-%25E3%2582%25B7%25E3%2583%25B3%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25AB%25E3%2581%25AAtodo%25E3%2583%25AA%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2583%2588-%25E3%2582%25BF%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2582%25AF%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E7%2590%2586%25E3%2582%25A2%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25AA/id626144601?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<h3 id=\"feedly\" style=\"position:relative;\">Feedly</h3>\n<p>好きなブログを登録しておくと、新しい記事が投稿されると通知がきます。</p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple114/v4/3e/ce/49/3ece4929-7e64-234f-241f-1b73e22748d7/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"Feedly - Smart News Reader\" class=\"appreach__icon\" style><div class=\"appreach__detail\" style><p class=\"appreach__name\">Feedly - Smart News Reader</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">Feedly Inc.</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\" style><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/feedly-smart-news-reader/id396069556?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"データ共有編\" style=\"position:relative;\">データ共有編</h2>\n<p>Mac、iPad、iPhoneだとデバイス間で文章、画像などをコピー＆ペーストできます。（同じApple IDでサインインしているデバイス同士だとできるみたい）</p>\n<p>私はこの機能、めっちゃ感動しました。\niPhoneで音声入力しといた文章をコピーして、Macにペーストして使っています。</p>\n<h3 id=\"air-drop\" style=\"position:relative;\">Air Drop</h3>\n<p>写真や書類を近くの人に送る時に使っています。\n例えば、打ち合わせのときに、ホワイトボードにメモを書く→写真を撮る→同席者のiPhoneにその場で共有。\n後からメール送信したりしなくていいので、すごく楽。</p>\n<h3 id=\"google-drive\" style=\"position:relative;\">Google Drive</h3>\n<p>チームでのプロジェクトなど、他の人とファイル共有するときに使っています。</p>\n<p>付属のGoogle DocumentやGoogle SpreadsheetもWordやExcelの代わりに使っています。</p>\n<h3 id=\"icloud-drive\" style=\"position:relative;\">iCloud Drive</h3>\n<p>個人用のファイルはiCloud Driveに入れます。</p>\n<p>Pages、NumbersなどMac専用の文書作成、表作成ツールも、Windowsとの互換性がイマイチなので、自分用の書類管理に使ってます。</p>\n<h3 id=\"evernote\" style=\"position:relative;\">Evernote</h3>\n<p>有名な文書管理アプリですね。\n手書きのノートを使い終わったときに、残したいページを写真で撮って保管しています。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 749px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 172%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ss evernote 20191115\"\n        title=\"ss evernote 20191115\"\n        src=\"/static/09b4a4cf0cb4add023ca7a6a96eccea7/29177/ss_evernote_20191115.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09b4a4cf0cb4add023ca7a6a96eccea7/e07e9/ss_evernote_20191115.jpg 200w,\n/static/09b4a4cf0cb4add023ca7a6a96eccea7/066f9/ss_evernote_20191115.jpg 400w,\n/static/09b4a4cf0cb4add023ca7a6a96eccea7/29177/ss_evernote_20191115.jpg 749w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"appreach\"><img src=\"https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/85/c9/e8/85c9e806-0333-885a-31bc-4d70dae9d6e0/source/512x512bb.jpg\" alt=\"Evernote\" class=\"appreach__icon\"><div class=\"appreach__detail\"><p class=\"appreach__name\">Evernote</p><p class=\"appreach__info\"><span class=\"appreach__developper\">Evernote</span><span class=\"appreach__price\">&#x7121;&#x6599;</span><span class=\"appreach__posted\">posted with<a href=\"https://mama-hack.com/app-reach/\" title=\"&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#x30A2;&#x30D7;&#x30EA;&#x30FC;&#x30C1;</a></span></p></div><div class=\"appreach__links\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/evernote/id281796108?uo=4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"appreach__aslink\"><img src=\"https://nabettu.github.io/appreach/img/itune_ja.svg\"></a></div></div>\n<h3 id=\"pocket\" style=\"position:relative;\">Pocket</h3>\n<p>ブログやwebを読んでて、後でも読みたいなっと思う記事をPocketに入れています。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"【仕事効率化】フリーランスにおすすめのアプリを紹介","date":"2019/11/15","updateDate":null,"des